 src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20181004/720pix/1538652486_eb8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20181004%2F720pix%2F1538652486_eb8c.jpg&h=10600e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2018/10/04/3706968/20181006_sub356NEWNEWNEWNEW_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F3706968%2F20181006_sub356NEWNEWNEWNEW_clean_w.mp4&d=mSaaklrB3SRJE07mHO5emgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0bfad142\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2018/10/04/3706968/20181006_sub356NEWNEWNEWNEW_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538565030_e6e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538565030_e6e4.jpg&h=4de705c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 華蓮絲愛欖球也愛寫作，這兩年埋首記錄香港老行業的專書終於出版。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538565033_2bea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538565033_2bea.jpg&h=0c917a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 玉器市場的寫信佬精通四國語言，教華蓮絲印象深刻。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538565030_7ee9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538565030_7ee9.jpg&h=a41349be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 華蓮絲跟小人婆成為朋友，小人婆即將退休湊孫也相告。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538565030_9b0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538565030_9b0c.jpg&h=e89a92f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 華蓮絲常路經位於中環唐樓樓梯底的印刷舖，於是決定訪問老闆。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538565034_e49b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538565034_e49b.jpg&h=8e84f749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 新書黑白封面 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538565636_6d30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538565636_6d30.jpg&h=1647d5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 她任全職欖球員13年，多次為香港衝鋒陷陣。 <br />\n <br />\nsource : <a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20181005/58752734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58752734&d=mSaaklrB3SRJE07mHO5emgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=58a56075\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58752734&h=da5b5c84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20181005/58752734</a><br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++"},{"pid":"979bba702ce1b7d61c389acb4db3fe6918fc321f","tid":848674,"uid":126769,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d6861d43df0d14a0497b476763e5c4916d4982d7","tid":848674,"uid":33875,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"1cdb86a7fa91db1c5df19792da66aeedfb4572bb","tid":848674,"uid":23758,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"成個POST關心條女個樣重多過關心香港文化同夕陽行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"然後話香港女仔膚淺"},"citedBy":0,"repl